genresAdvancedInfo.name: son jarocho
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Son jarocho is a traditional music genre from Veracruz, Mexico. It features a mix of indigenous, Spanish, and African rhythms and instruments, including the jarana, requinto, and harp. The lyrics often focus on social and political issues, as well as love and nature.
